## 3. Ganti `quizMeta`

```javascript
const PAKET_ICONS = ['📘','📗','📙','📕','📔','📒','📃','📄','📑','🗒️'];
const quizMeta = Array.from({length:TOTAL_PAKET},(_,i)=>({
  id: i+1,
  name: `Paket ${i+1}`,
  icon: PAKET_ICONS[i] || '📋'
}));
