## 5. Ganti semua loop lain yang pakai `i<=5`

Cari dan ganti di fungsi-fungsi ini:

| Fungsi | Ganti |
|---|---|
| `refreshAkunPage` | `i<=5` → `i<=TOTAL_PAKET` |
| `getBadgeStats` | `i<=5` → `i<=TOTAL_PAKET` |
| `refreshStatistik` | `i<=5` → `i<=TOTAL_PAKET` |
| `mulaiSimulasi` | `i<=5` → `i<=TOTAL_PAKET` |
| `resetAllProgress` | `i<=5` → `i<=TOTAL_PAKET` |

